<title>UK: Siebe has 9.7 percent of APV.</title>
<headline>Siebe has 9.7 percent of APV.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>UK engineering group Siebe Plc said on Tuesday that it bought 20 million ordinary shares in APV Plc at 107.46p per share in the market today.</p>
<p>This latest purchase brings Siebe's holding in APV, a process engineering company, to 28.9 million shares or 9.7 percent.</p>
<p>Siebe made a 327.4 million stg recommended offer for APV on May 9. The offer of 0.10955 new Siebe shares for eacg APV share values APV shares at around 105p but there is a cash alternative of 97.5p per APV share.</p>
<p>--London Newsroom +44 171 542 4019</p>
